Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:15.47,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}手を伸ばして　焦がれていた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:19.55,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}届くはずない　光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:23.51,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}こんな世界で　こんな世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:26.10,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}何度も見てた夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:37.69,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}君の割れた　硝子細工
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:41.41,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur4}触れた指が　痛いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:45.66,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}大切なもの　要らないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:48.48,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}元には戻せない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:53.34,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}愛　一雫　頬を濡らして
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:56.26,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}切なく　雨が降る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:04:01.67,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}まだ何も君を知らないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:05.72,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}その涙が　止まったなら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:09.52,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}笑ってみてほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:13.86,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}あ憧れて　憧れて　想像を形へと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:17.72,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}変えるリアリティ　空を駆けて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:22.00,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}行くよ　窓の外は君を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.91,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}連れ出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:26.47,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}真っ暗な雲が去って
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:31.05,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}残した水面に　映る色は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:37.67,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨上がり　君は　君の目で答えを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:40.80,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}探してほしい
Comment: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:12.43,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,OP-CN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:15.47,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我所伸出的手　如此急不可耐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:19.55,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}那所无法传达　光芒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:23.51,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}在如此的天地里　在这样的世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:26.10,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}浮生若梦　回眸几何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:37.69,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}你所制作的　玻璃饰品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:41.41,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur4}指尖一触　寸心如割
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:45.66,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}必不可少的　不再所需的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:48.48,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}至始至终　覆水难收
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:53.34,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}爱　仅需一滴　脸颊便能浸润
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:56.26,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}心如刀绞　雨恨云愁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:04:01.67,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我还是对你　一无所知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:05.72,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那些落泪　就此止泣的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:09.52,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}多想与你　欢声笑语
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:13.86,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}如此憧憬　如此向往　想象便形成力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:17.72,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}就能改变当下　于晴空翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:22.00,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一起出发吧　窗外的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.91,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}携手与你共赏春秋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:26.47,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}黑云已散　风光日霁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:31.05,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨后镜花水月　依旧彩虹色映
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:37.67,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨过天晴的你　眼眸自知物理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:40.80,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}不过我想让你　所寻自己而已
